| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7745 — Recovery Inhibition (alphalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4ee28743-f73f-5045-9e1b-8fb916389cdc"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
